Version: 0.6
Release: alt1

Summary: Math extension for Python-Markdown
License: BSD
Group:   Development/Python3
URL:     https://github.com/mitya57/python-markdown-math

Packager: Andrey Cherepanov <cas@altlinux.org>

BuildRequires(pre): rpm-build-python3
